          <a class="indexterm" name="PsionicMonsters233"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Burst (Su):</strong></span> Three times per day, a <a href="ch77s29.html#PsionicMonsters231">xeph</a> can increase his or her speed by 10 feet, plus 10 feet per four character levels beyond 1st, to a maximum increase of 30 feet at 9th character level and higher. These bursts of speed are considered a competence bonus to the <a href="ch77s29.html#PsionicMonsters231">xeph's</a> base speed. A burst of speed lasts 3 rounds.</p>
          <p>The <a href="ch77s29.html#PsionicMonsters231">xeph</a> warrior presented here had the following ability scores before racial adjustments: Str 13, Dex 11, Con 12, Int 10, Wis 9, Cha 8.</p>
        </div>
