        <p><a href="ch77s29.html#PsionicMonsters231">Xeph</a> characters possess the following racial traits.</p>
        <div class="itemizedlist">
          <ul type="bullet">
            <li style="list-style-type: disc">
              <p>-2 Strength, +2 Dexterity.</p>
