              <p><a href="ch22.html#CombatII28">Medium</a> size.</p>
            </li>
            <li style="list-style-type: disc">
              <p><a href="ch77s29.html#PsionicMonsters231">Xeph</a> base land <a href="ch21s02.html#CombatI14">speed</a> is 30 feet.</p>
