            <li style="list-style-type: disc">
              <p>Darkvision out to 60 feet.</p>
            </li>
            <li style="list-style-type: disc">
              <p>Naturally Psionic: <a href="ch77s29.html#PsionicMonsters231">Xephs</a> gain 1 bonus power point at 1st level.</p>
